    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "This can be solved by using sortBy with a parseFloat (otherwise it sorts alphabetically). As using numerical values for facets is not the main use case (because it usually will explode quickly in number of values, making a range more interesting), I'll close this issue for now. ",
